{"tid":1432824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好俾Youtube淪為藍絲洗腦工具","createTime":"2019-08-08T10:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T18:00:32.000Z","uid":301467,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef8ef98e65fd367ca785acd77c79d91a87330f9","tid":1432824,"uid":301467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"有時youtube會睇政治野 一路都好少見有政治廣告<br />\n但最近見藍絲廢佬d fb page開始係youtube落廣告<br />\n企圖將我地渲染成俾人洗腦既後生仔<br />\n咁樣班人就會更加唔理我地講野既內容合唔合理<br />\n只會一黎就否定我地<br />\n咁我地成功說服人地由藍轉黃既機會就降低<br />\n大家覺得應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSWzrEH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSWzrEH.png&h=0a26c18a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c73cb625414a01589b1829ee19a118886c1179b","tid":1432824,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"好多人以為FB比嬲嬲或者YouTube比Dislike就可以令對家收皮<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dudekT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dudekT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac5a631f1574c2a2451cb4861307706a161dc144","tid":1432824,"uid":281567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"有無人知youtube廣告幾錢先可以落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ea6abca9d732451bba991e8f9c173b5faf7ab9","tid":1432824,"uid":282733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"反對Youtube播放政治洗腦廣告！"},{"pid":"65cae00b66115922ae252b2aa5d9d24566a0adde","tid":1432824,"uid":41576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"原來環保團體都有connect埋？ 文宣講埋催淚彈損兒童腦部發展？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1433442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1433442</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d91ec8130fa0d63aac923a9ec718f26326e41e1a","tid":1432824,"uid":239742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019